          "Comments",
          "Limitations"
        ],
        [
          "Higher Education",
          "Project-Based \nLearning",
          "Content-Based Filtering",
          "Lessons deemed useful for learner’s current Capstone Project",
          "311 students",
          "3 editions of a Capstone Course",
          "Lessons learned by previous students.\n\nLessons are represented by Emdeddings.\n\nThere is no representation of the users. Instead it is solely based on the content provided. ",
          "Embeddings",
          "Recommendations for a given query are only changed aftert model retraining.",
          "Performed at the ESP level: html parsing, tonization and stopword removal.\n\nEmbeddings are created using Mulltilingual BERT.\n\nFeedback on the interaction  between users and content is given by rating.",
          "Top-N Lessons",
          "{Relevancy: 3.28 - Transformer, Transparency: 3.77 - Transformer, Novelty: 3.34 - Transformer, Serendipity: 3.12 - Transformer) ",
          "Authors present Kanban, an educational platform whose aim is to assist in the development of a capstone project. \n\nAuthors perform 2 distinct experiments with learners: \n\n1 - 4 Consultations on  Course Contents on the RS\n\n2- Interact with the Chatbot that is meant to go beyond what the simple RS does.\n\n\nResults on student ratings highlight that there are statistically signifcant differences between the proposed transformer model and the LSI baseline (except serendipity).",
          "- Cannot use external sources of knowledge, \n\n- No analysis of pending tasks, \n\n"
        ]
      ],
      "index": 5
    }
  ],
