    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-80e6-a644-c6107a996768",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The study tries to bridge the gap by combining recommender systems with Chatbot AI assistants. Experiments are conducted but the results are not mentioned in the abstract. ",
